{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"faede56c8b","title":"对《红旗》杂志社论稿《论革命的“三结合”》的批语和修改","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f3de70ad45","index":0,"year":1967,"month":3,"day":7,"articleId":"faede56c8b","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"革命委员会","id":"1d084c925f","type":"主题"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"f926fef802","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"faede56c8b","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这篇社论稿是由中共中央文化革命小组组员、《红旗》杂志副总编辑王力、关锋撰写的。1967年3月2日，中共中央文化革命小组组长、《红旗》杂志总编辑陈伯达将这篇社论稿送毛泽东审阅时写道：“革命的三结合方针和正确对待干部问题，得到广大群众拥护。同时，有些人也在利用这个问题，搞复辟活动。针对这种情况，王力、关锋同志拟了一篇社论，南说主席的革命三结合方针，以便引起注意。本篇一是毛泽东写在送审稿上的批语：本篇二是毛泽东在社论稿中加写的话。这篇社论在1967年3月30日出版的《红旗》杂志第五期上发表，《人民日报》3月10日提前转载。"},{"id":"81c1ce2312","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"faede56c8b","publication":{},"article":{},"index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"林彪，在中共八届十一中全会上继续当选为中央政治局常委，不久被称中央副主席。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8c0f432288","type":"title","text":"对《红旗》杂志社论稿《论革命的“三结合”》的批语和修改！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"faede56c8b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f926fef802","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪同志阅后，退文革小组","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"faede56c8b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"81c1ce2312","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"faede56c8b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"457bce61b6","type":"paragraph","text":"三月七日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"faede56c8b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b31b1b66bc","type":"paragraph","text":"从上至下，凡要夺权的单位，都要有军队或民兵参加，组成“三结合”。不论工厂、农村、财贸、文教（大、中、小学）、党政机关及民众团体都要这样做。县以上都派军队代表，公社以下都派民兵代表，这是非常之好的。军队代表不足，可以暂缺，将来再派","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"faede56c8b","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":355,"end":354}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0032c856b0","type":"paragraph","text":"1967.03.07","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"faede56c8b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"09eaf89293","type":"title","text":"对《红旗》杂志社论稿《论革命的“三结合”》的批语和修改","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"faede56c8b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"646ef17f4b","type":"paragraph","text":"从上至下，凡要夺权的单位，都要有军队或民兵参加，组成“三结合”。不论工厂、农村、财贸、文教（大、中、小学）、党政机关及民众团体都要这样做。县以上都派军队代表，公社以下都派民兵代表，这是非常之好的。军队代表不足，可以暂缺，将来再派。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"faede56c8b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7e44022bc5","type":"paragraph","text":"对《红旗》杂志社论稿《论革命的“三结合”》的批语和修改","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"faede56c8b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d073b91845","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"faede56c8b","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}